ated": 1603854684, "last_modified": 1639014545}, "last_reply_by": "qiaoqiao1235", "last_touched": 1641865359, "title": "看见大家在鄙视 QQ 的软件大小，有没有人记得夸克浏览器呢", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827235", "created": 1641780808, "deleted": 0, "content": "夸克应该在小众浏览器里算很火的了，我是从刚开始公测（上架 app store ）就开始一直用到现在的用户。作为 UI 还多次找客服反馈 bug 或意见（后来夸克的客服从邮件反馈变成了外包给阿里的客服，我就放弃了）\r\n大家可以打开手机的存储，看看现在你手机里夸克浏览器的 app 大小，原来标榜做最小最简单的纯净浏览器，后面更新了好多“额外”的功能，比如语音助手、比如夸克的云盘等等等等。。。\r\n当然用户是很多面的，不同的用户对同一款软件有不同的需求。所以也想问问大家对于夸克近几年更新还有产品方向的看法，不知道大家实际上用不用夸克这些“额外”的功能、对于软件和产品的“初心”都可以探讨", "content_rendered": "夸克应该在小众浏览器里算很火的了，我是从刚开始公测（上架 app store ）就开始一直用到现在的用户。作为 UI 还多次找客服反馈 bug 或意见（后来夸克的客服从邮件反馈变成了外包给阿里的客服，我就放弃了）<br />大家可以打开手机的存储，看看现在你手机里夸克浏览器的 app 大小，原来标榜做最小最简单的纯净浏览器，后面更新了好多“额外”的功能，比如语音助手、比如夸克的云盘等等等等。。。<br />当然用户是很多面的，不同的用户对同一款软件有不同的需求。所以也想问问大家对于夸克近几年更新还有产品方向的看法，不知道大家实际上用不用夸克这些“额外”的功能、对于软件和产品的“初心”都可以探讨", "last_modified": 1641780808, "replies": 56, "id": 827235}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_large.png?m=1563424621", "name": "fe", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_normal.png?m=1563424621", "title": "前端开发", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/fe", "topics": 2371, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Frontend", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_mini.png?m=1563424621", "stars": 1126, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 791, "parent_node_name": "programmer"}, "member": {"id": 7928, "username": "wudaown", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wudaown", "website": "http://wudaown.wordpress.com", "twitter": "wudaown", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d6b35a889d4ac3c99eeb9e8eae72c2c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d6b35a889d4ac3c99eeb9e8eae72c2c?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d6b35a889d4ac3c99eeb9e8eae72c2c?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1302693322, "last_modified": 1302779988}, "last_reply_by": "jguo", "last_touched": 1641845823, "title": "React HTTP 请求问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827424", "created": 1641820446, "deleted": 0, "content": "各位大佬，\r\n\r\n目前在开发某项目，希望后端不能被外网访问\r\n\r\n前端和外网是通的，可以访问\r\n\r\n前端的机器和后端机器在同一个内网\r\n\r\n现在希望用户访问前端后由前端的机器发起请求而不是从用户网络发起请求。\r\n\r\n\r\n大佬们 这个能做到吗。。\r\n\r\n开发完了 今天测试才想起来网络请求是从用户网络出去的。。这我就很尴尬了。。", "content_rendered": "<p>各位大佬，</p>\n<p>目前在开发某项目，希望后端不能被外网访问</p>\n<p>前端和外网是通的，可以访问</p>\n<p>前端的机器和后端机器在同一个内网</p>\n<p>现在希望用户访问前端后由前端的机器发起请求而不是从用户网络发起请求。</p>\n<p>大佬们 这个能做到吗。。</p>\n<p>开发完了 今天测试才想起来网络请求是从用户网络出去的。。这我就很尴尬了。。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1641820547, "replies": 50, "id": 827424}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1543/843a/395_large.png?m=1466398352", "name": "opensource", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1543/843a/395_normal.png?m=1466398352", "title": "开源软件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/opensource", "topics": 303, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Open Source", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1543/843a/395_mini.png?m=1466398352", "stars": 267, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 395, "parent_node_name": "programmer"}, "member": {"id": 354931, "username": "aboat365", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/aboat365", "website": "https://aboat365.com/", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8bd11beb5b34ac9aa904ad229e5679d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8bd11beb5b34ac9aa904ad229e5679d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f8bd11beb5b34ac9aa904ad229e5679d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1539135057, "last_modified": 1539135057}, "last_reply_by": "holinhot", "last_touched": 1641847380, "title": "开源，是否是一门生意？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827256", "created": 1641784461, "deleted": 0, "content": "Faker.js 删库事件有感。先声明本人是名普通程序员，偶尔维护开源项目，在工作中也使用大量的开源程序。天下熙熙皆为利来，天下攘攘皆为利往，如果站在利益（中性词）的角度来观察开源，就能看到不一样的世界。本人认为，开源就是一门生意，Faker.js 的作者只是一个生意失败的人。  \r\n纵观开源界，确实人才济济，有各种厉害的项目，但成功背后都有资本的影子。开源世界，并非是世外桃源，反而是一个毫无规则，毫无底线的修罗场。大多数的开源项目，就如同那河里的鹅卵石，随波逐流。漂亮的鹅卵石偶尔会被小孩子发现拾起，更多只是被捞起碾碎成了混凝土，大多数直接淹没在历史的断层里。  \r\n最后，我只是一个玩泥巴的人，希望有人一起来玩泥巴。", "content_rendered": "<p>Faker.js 删库事件有感。先声明本人是名普通程序员，偶尔维护开源项目，在工作中也使用大量的开源程序。天下熙熙皆为利来，天下攘攘皆为利往，如果站在利益（中性词）的角度来观察开源，就能看到不一样的世界。本人认为，开源就是一门生意，Faker.js 的作者只是一个生意失败的人。<br/>\n纵观开源界，确实人才济济，有各种厉害的项目，但成功背后都有资本的影子。开源世界，并非是世外桃源，反而是一个毫无规则，毫无底线的修罗场。大多数的开源项目，就如同那河里的鹅卵石，随波逐流。漂亮的鹅卵石偶尔会被小孩子发现拾起，更多只是被捞起碾碎成了混凝土，大多数直接淹没在历史的断层里。<br/>\n最后，我只是一个玩泥巴的人，希望有人一起来玩泥巴。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1641855847, "replies": 48, "id": 827256}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/5d61/6dd3/1017_large.png?m=1641688488", "name": "blockchain", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/5d61/6dd3/1017_normal.png?m=1641688488", "title": "区块链", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/blockchain", "topics": 454, "footer": "", "header": "关于区块链技术的开发和应用的讨论。", "title_alternative": "Blockchain", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/5d61/6dd3/1017_mini.png?m=1641688488", "stars": 453, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1017, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 55793, "username": "TangMonk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/TangMonk", "website": "", "twitter": "TangMonk", "psn": "", "github": "TangMonk", "btc": "", "location": "成都", "tagline": "Mercy and Peaceful", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e996e6bd8780ea2cace5c7dcec065050?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e996e6bd8780ea2cace5c7dcec065050?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e996e6bd8780ea2cace5c7dcec065050?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1392206286, "last_modified": 1392206286}, "last_reply_by": "newmlp", "last_touched": 1641841200, "title": "可否把钱长期存放在以太坊上？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827392", "created": 1641809622, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1641809622, "replies": 45, "id": 827392}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 47038, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451", "stars": 7660, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 492781, "username": "3kkkk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/3kkkk", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/03148694115f50c36ddb90678f8cc317?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/03148694115f50c36ddb90678f8cc317?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/03148694115f50c36ddb90678f8cc317?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1591083598, "last_modified": 1640932111}, "last_reply_by": "xuanbg", "last_touched": 1641828578, "title": "拼多多没有购物车，购物车是伪需求吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827246", "created": 1641782882, "deleted": 0, "content": "上学写的项目代码最早就是购物车，用购物网站也习惯购物车的存在。直到拼多多出现才发现原来最电商可以这样，批发市场不需要购物车。", "content_rendered": "<p>上学写的项目代码最早就是购物车，用购物网站也习惯购物车的存在。直到拼多多出现才发现原来最电商可以这样，批发市场不需要购物车。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1641782882, "replies": 43, "id": 827246}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1635652519", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1635652519", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 17754, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1635652519", "stars": 4508, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 538650, "username": "Guillotine", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Guillotine", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a25198c7cde757bf1d8accd3550cda11?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a25198c7cde757bf1d8accd3550cda11?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a25198c7cde757bf1d8accd3550cda11?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1616243197, "last_modified": 1616243197}, "last_reply_by": "Tenlearn", "last_touched": 1641865691, "title": "好烦啊， Mac 为什么没有一个完美的浏览器？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827395", "created": 1641810452, "deleted": 0, "content": "Macbook air M1 下，每个浏览器都有不完美的地方，强迫症好难受。\r\n\r\nSafari：全家桶标签页同步和阅读清单很爽，但插件太少，看 YouTube 都没有可以设置默认最高分辨率，以及下拉边刷评论边小窗口看视频的插件，比如 Enhancer for youtube 那种。\r\n\r\nFirefox：喜欢 container 以及全局画中画，但看 B 站加载不了弹幕。\r\n\r\nChrome: 没有明显缺点，但也没有吸引我去用的点。真的要放弃同步从 Safari 转到 chrome 吗？\r\n\r\nVivaldi：个人定制真香，平滑滚动是我用过最平滑的，就是每次打开新标签页都要闪屏，在当前标签页输入新地址后也是，卸载了。\r\n\r\nBrave：跟 Vivaldi 一样有闪屏\r\n\r\nEdge：跟 chrome 一样，没有吸引我去用的点。", "content_rendered": "<p>Macbook air M1 下，每个浏览器都有不完美的地方，强迫症好难受。</p>\n<p>Safari：全家桶标签页同步和阅读清单很爽，但插件太少，看 YouTube 都没有可以设置默认最高分辨率，以及下拉边刷评论边小窗口看视频的插件，比如 Enhancer for youtube 那种。</p>\n<p>Firefox：喜欢 container 以及全局画中画，但看 B 站加载不了弹幕。</p>\n<p>Chrome: 没有明显缺点，但也没有吸引我去用的点。真的要放弃同步从 Safari 转到 chrome 吗？</p>\n<p>Vivaldi：个人定制真香，平滑滚动是我用过最平滑的，就是每次打开新标签页都要闪屏，在当前标签页输入新地址后也是，卸载了。</p>\n<p>Brave：跟 Vivaldi 一样有闪屏</p>\n<p>Edge：跟 chrome 一样，没有吸引我去用的点。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1641810762, "replies": 42, "id": 827395}]